      <title>PAI 探索 100 亿美元雀巢冰淇淋合资企业的选择</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-12/pai-said-to-explore-options-for-10-billion-nestle-ice-cream-jv</link>
